{"tid":1800573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際線行動] 29/12有集會究竟有冇人知????","createTime":"2019-12-28T03:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T15:51:15.000Z","uid":192306,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e3f20d71bb8810dee2460d8af50d8391b9709e06","tid":1800573,"uid":192306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:13:35.000Z","msg":"《香港人抗爭的日與夜》集會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">日期: 2019 年 12月29日<br />\n時間: 1400-2000<br />\n地點: 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n已有不反對通知書</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我們將於2019年12月29日假中環愛丁堡廣場舉行「香港人抗爭的日與夜」集會。 本集會期望透過不同嘉賓的分享以及紀錄片，與眾多香港人<span style=\"color: red;\">回顧過去六個月的抗爭之路，並向政府重申我們的訴求。</span><br />\n<br />\n另外，我們亦製作了一幅3 x 38米、以及印有運動歷程及反送中運動口號三部份的演變：加油、反抗以及報仇的<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂布供眾多市民簽署</span>，並留下各自的心聲。其後，<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂布將會寄到世界各地</span>，讓各地的香港人，甚至是外國人了解我們於這六個月裡所經歷的血與淚。<br />\n<br />\n我們希望各位能夠「毋忘殤痛 誓爭自由」，一起努力繼續抗爭！<br />\n<br />\n香港人堅持！<br />\n<br />\n頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/HKProtesters1229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKProtesters1229&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPDk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=f11cbca3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKProtesters1229</a><br />\n公海: <a href=\"http://t.me/HK_Protesters1229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHK_Protesters1229&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPDk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=121f8738\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/HK_Protesters1229</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SUh3Hst.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSUh3Hst.jpg&h=e9fece39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">個活動算係半個國際線任務啦</span></span>！過嚟簽個名寫幾句都好，嚟埋集會就仲好，求下大家，好多日程表都冇呢個活動，幫推俾人知好嗎香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽日就係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de101851984f1039f7dd863b6914d5a605afcc7","tid":1800573,"uid":192306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:13:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fbd0b61cc851c20857eddb20735a4ccf52a0be56","tid":1800573,"uid":192306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:14:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4f1bd846d66577632ce06601181212ecbd4d908e","tid":1800573,"uid":192306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:14:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e00f430600e9ca78b4348637ef98bd707ac93eb4","tid":1800573,"uid":192306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:15:13.000Z","msg":"屌你哋咁得閒笑人哋個女可唔可以做下實際嘢"},{"pid":"7df10e89ba19800efbccd32cbf4267163509fc23","tid":1800573,"uid":192306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:15:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2fb624561c3dbbeacf9ffe7e70900d274ae03e46","tid":1800573,"uid":192306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:16:09.000Z","msg":"聽日呀"},{"pid":"c4d1f6a97117e863b4a2b59222ed177a5ea9ea46","tid":1800573,"uid":192306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:16:29.000Z","msg":"聽日見好唔好"},{"pid":"c33aae1707ab357b4fc28b7a9ba06871eb7690c5","tid":1800573,"uid":192306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:16:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0acd12c77a3720ece5a33185b6a8403c04d76e11","tid":1800573,"uid":192306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:17:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M6q8TAo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM6q8TAo.jpg&h=59fae523&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f99534f9ede8c6dccad6f929038deb03d86572c","tid":1800573,"uid":192306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:17:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ccd32df19b9b596